Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak tinggal di hutan ini,\Nsudah beberapa kali musim dingin datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena setiap tahun\Nsalju menumpuk cukup tebal,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami tak bertani di musim ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hidup memanfaatkan persediaan makanan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kayu bakar yang sudah kami siapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tahun ini ada desa baru,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jumlah penduduk makin banyak,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sempat cemas persediaan tak cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanan di sana tidak berkurang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, bukan berarti\Ntidak berkurang sama sekali,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi konsumsi mereka sangat sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dihitung, konsumsi mereka\Nsepertiga dari perkiraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:00:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konsumsinya hanya sepertiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya, itu karena pengalaman\Ndan kebiasaan hidup mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka terbiasa menghemat makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidup sederhana memang bagus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kalau terlalu menahan diri\Njuga kurang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah bilang tak perlu menahan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana kalau minta bantu habiskan\Nmakanan yang cepat basi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seperti sayur dan daging?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, mungkin itu bisa membujuk mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita segara sampaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita juga perlu cek persediaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NApa para Nyunyudaphne ada masalah juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalahnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada masalah sama sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka tak butuh makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berubah jadi pohon\Nsaat musim dingin pun bukan kendala.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kadang kami harus menggali mereka\Nkarena terkubur salju.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya aku mendapatkan tugas,\Ntapi tidak ada yang bisa kuurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang dulu, anggap saja mereka semua\Nmerasa tenang karena ada kamu di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada satu hal lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada permintaan dari para Minotaurus\Nuntuk Nyunyudaphne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka minta pakailah baju\Nkalau sedang di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, saat berubah jadi manusia,\Nmereka lupa pakai baju.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, pasti akan kusampaikan ke mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah masalahnya cuma sepele.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena musim dingin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami buat makanan khas musim dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, matangnya pas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aroma harum nasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kamu masak sesuatu yang beda, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian peka, ya?\NAtau hidung kalian tajam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian buat banyak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau buat onigiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kira-kira berapa banyak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, hari ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian terlalu polos, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa tiba-tiba begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pasti persiapan fermentasi jenis baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, dari sini hasilnya akan beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau mulai apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya mau buat masakan baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita akan menumbuk moci\Ndengan lesung dan alu ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lesung dan alu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang dipegang itu alu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beras itu akan jadi moci?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beras?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara membuatnya saja sudah rumit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata cara makannya juga beragam, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beras ini juga bukan beras biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini beras khusus untuk moci.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Moci, moci, moci, moci.\N- Ternyata ada jenisnya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita mulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pukul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pukul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pukul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pikir mereka akan melakukan\Ncara yang lebih spesial...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata cukup sederhana, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lumayan melelahkan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Caranya dipukul sampai halus, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau coba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pelan-pelan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, aku mulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balikkan lalu ulen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu dulu, ada reaksi bahaya muncul!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah jadi bahan yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulangi dan fokus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah semuanya datang\Ndan bergantian mencoba,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}perlahan mereka bisa\Nmenumbuk moci dengan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf menunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bahan peledak yang mungkin\Ntak akan sampai menghancurkan rumah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, hilangkan ide meledakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah susah payah, moci akhirnya jadi\Ndan disajikan dengan banyak rasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada rasa gula kecap manis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kinako klasik,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu zunda dari edamane yang dihaluskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teksturnya jadi seperti ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis dan asin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harumnya terasa dan juga lembut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, zenzai dari kacang merah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di musim dingin begini,\Nhangatnya sangat terasa, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu panas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau, silakan cicipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, moci daun, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami campur ini dengan daun harum dari hutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga enak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih segar dari mugwort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang kalau kalian suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, mengambil daunnya agak susah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami harus siaga kalau diserang balik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daunnya bisa menyerang balik?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jauh beda dari onigiri, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata beras itu unik, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kalian memasak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Donovan.\NItu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar kalian sedang memasak\Ndari bahan beras.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kubawakan minuman yang pas untuk kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Doburoku yang dibuat dari beras, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sake, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian langsung tahu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, silakan coba rasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Wah!\N- Asyik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini rasanya lumayan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, menumbuk moci\Ndi hari cerah menjadi tren,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekaligus mengatasi kurangnya\Nkegiatan selama musim dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, yang paling jago menumbuk moci
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah Gordon dari ras Minotaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak perlu pakai banyak tenaga,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cukup angkat alunya lalu pukul ke bawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isekai Nonbiri Nouka 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mohon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadilah istriku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu, kamu siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kepala keluarga Marquis Britoa\Ndari Kerajaan Iblis Gargard,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Glatts Britoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh beri tahu namamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Ronana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita Minotaurus dari Desa Kedua
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan pria besar berzirah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf malah jadi merepotkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke Desa Pohon Besar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa mendadak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Relasi dengan desa itu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat penting bagi Kerajaan Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar kalau aku ingin melihatnya langsung!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia ngotot,\Naku bawa dia ke sini, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah jatuh cinta\Npada pandangan pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kamu kadesnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku Hiraku, kades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa syaratnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri tahu syarat\Nagar aku bisa menikahi Ronana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dengar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia perlu izin Kades agar bisa\Nmenjawab lamaranku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa melamar biasanya begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kadang ada yang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi biasanya yang merestui itu\Norang tua mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beda lagi kalau istri kedua atau ketiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada suatu hari,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seorang bangsawan muda bertemu\Ngadis dari desa pelosok.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah mendongeng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta beda status.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua orang yang terpisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malam gelap tanpa bulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua lari
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dikejar tangan jahat Kades!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kira-kira seperti itu dogengnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ada hal yang aku paham\Ndan juga tidak paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mengakui kesungguhanmu,\Ntapi yang terpenting itu perasaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Ronana tidak mau,\Naku tak bisa merestui pernikahan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, bagaimana kalau dia\Nsetuju ingin menikah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melarang ada paksaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dilarang ada kekerasan\Natau mengancam dengan kekuasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkan dengan matang dan renungkan\Napa dia orang yang pantas untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama kalian mematuhi itu,\Ntidak ada lagi yang perlu kukatakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, Ronana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertemuannya tiba-tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kuharapkan,\Nsemoga ini berjalan dengan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami mulai dari saling\Nberkirim surat, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa berhenti memikirkannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau terus begini,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia bisa saja diambil pria lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin ada di sisinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mundur dari Empat Jenderal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu itu jenderal pasukan Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak bisa seenaknya meninggalkan tugas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penggantinya kuserahkan pada adikku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar tak bertanggung jawab!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak peduli!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu harusnya malu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hidup demi cinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku juga berhenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bertindak seenaknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, sudah matang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini acar yang kami buat bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya matangnya pas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perbaikan panci yang diminta sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau nori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nori?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku bukan antusias seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Warnanya gelap dan bentuknya tipis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seberapa kuat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentuknya seperti rumput laut kombu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}biasanya dipakai untuk membungkus makanan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibungkus lalu dimakan? Kedengarannya ganas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak salah,\Ntumbuhnya di bebatuan tepi laut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konon panennya juga saat\Nmusim dingin seperti sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah dengar itu\Ndari idola yang bertani di TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dari laut,\Nmungkin kita bisa tanya ke Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti berkunjung ke Kota Sashato, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa hari kemudian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih selalu bermitra dengan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf malah merepotkanmu\Ndi tengah cuaca dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi urusan bisnis,\Nmau di tengah api atau air,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau diterpa angin utara kencang pun,\Nbukan masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, tentang rumput nori yang kamu cari,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami tak ada kebiasaan memakannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku tidak yakin apa ini rumputnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sebenarnya kurang begitu paham,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mari kita coba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, tumbuk lalu cincang dengan pisau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin sebegini cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu, campur air
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tuangkan ke cetakan kayu seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebegini cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini terlihat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seperti lumut di hutan gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah dipikir,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}memang disebutnya lumut laut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah diratakan tipis,\Nlepaskan cetakan kayunya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu keringkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita biarkan seperti ini saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita jemur di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kali ini kita akan minta bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Tia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku siap kapan pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keringlah, keringlah, mengeringlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir memang sangat membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah mengolah nori\Nyang kamu kumpulkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rumput lautnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kain?\NAtau kertas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan makanan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi langsung dimakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita panaskan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu jadi nori panggang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nori lebih mudah dicerna kalau dipanaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga agar semuanya tidak sakit perut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Warnanya mulai berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aroma yang belum pernah kuhirup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau norinya sudah matang...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus ditambah nasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu ditambah apa pun lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya sangat nostalgia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya membuatku ingin menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa seenak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa asinnya pas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya bisa dimakan juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dipegang sambil makan juga enak, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada nori, ada panggangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus buat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Moci isobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Moci yang sudah enak jadi renyah dan harum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kades, kalau mau,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami bisa mengurus pengambilan\Ndan pengolahan nori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gantinya, kami ingin barter\Nsebagian bahan moci ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa langsung barter karena\Nharus menanam beras ketannya dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kudiskusikan dengan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon bantuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahannya tahan lama, cara masaknya pun\Ncukup dipanggang dan diberi saus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sepertinya bisa jadi produk yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya, kudengar ada sake dari beras juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sake tidak boleh dibarter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isekai Nonbiri Nouka 2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada nasi, ada nori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuatu dalam diriku berteriak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buat susyi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa harus dikipas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku juga tidak tahu,\Ntapi suasananya lebih cocok begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nasi putih diberi cuka,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dicampur garam dan gula,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu gulung dan jadilah nasi susyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya susyi yang dibuat itu susyi nigiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi penduduk di dunia ini\Ntidak suka ikan mentah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi kali ini aku akan membuat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}susyi futomaki tanpa bahan mentah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, tikar gulung untuk susyi ini
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dibuatkan oleh para elf gunung yang terampil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah semua bahannya\Nditaruh di atas nasi, kita gulung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah digulung, potong seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata memotong rapi susah juga, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lumayan bagus juga ternyata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, membuat rasa lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada mayones juga,\Nsekalian buat salad gulung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tak ada kepiting olahan,\Nkami pakai daging kepiting asli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentuknya sangat mewah,\Nmustahil rasanya tidak enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian ini potongan yang gagal...\NAku cuma icip-icip saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sepertinya aku gagal memotongnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Naku pilih yang sudutnya kurang pas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makan tanpa izin itu tidak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, jadi ini susyi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentuknya cantik dan lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku agak kaget karena aromanya asam,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ternyata rasanya pas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami pakai cuka, jadi bisa dijadikan bekal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuka itu bisa membunuh kuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka pasti menyesal\Nkarena tak bisa tumbuh berkembang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti akan kubalas, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak terasa, musim dingin hampir berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cuaca dingin tetap bisa datang.\NMeski saljunya sudah mencair,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap tahun, aku selalu bingung kapan\Nwaktu yang tepat untuk mulai bertani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih terlalu awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai sekarang, aku akan ikut saran mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}beberapa hal harus dipersiapkan.\NSebelum musim semi datang,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalan keliling sambil bawa hiasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasang bahan peledak\Ndi sekitar kota lalu ledakkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dikejar sapi liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa harus repot melakukan hal berbahaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku juga tidak tahu kenapa.\NKalau ditanya begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, apa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang ada Desa Kedua dan Ketiga,\Npenduduknya juga bertambah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terpikirkan ingin mengadakan festival desa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu aku coba jelaskan festival\Nyang kutahu pada mereka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saling melempar tomat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengejar keju yang menggelinding di bukit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lari sambil bawa puding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, meski sudah dijelaskan,\Nkami masih belum paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa, aku yang salah karena\Nmenjelaskan festival yang aneh-aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, festival umum\Nmenurut kalian itu seperti apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin festival tahun baru\Natau perayaan panen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kalau itu lebih mudah dipahami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu biasanya apa yang kalian lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memasang Pyoppyo di tengah kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Muumuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kan pas Festival Musim Gugur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak paham mereka bahas apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tak paham,\Nkalau di dunia ini ada festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin lebih baik serahkan\Nke mereka untuk mengurusnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di daerah kami,\NPyoppyo keluar dari pusat kota
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu menyerang rumah para orang kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pyoppyo cuma menggali lubang,\Nyang menyerang itu Muumuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mereka menyerangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerang diam-diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Muumuu tak akan melakukan hal seperti itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah terjadi perbedaan versi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kalau menurut versi resmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cuma klaim sepihak, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Muumuu punya sisi adil!\N- Mereka malah debat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- apa kita bisa membuat mereka kompak?\N- Yang kacau dan garang itu Muumuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sepertinya sulit.\N- Yang kacau dan garang itu Muumuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tiap daerah punya versi yang berbeda jauh.\N- Muumuu itu mengalahkan hati yang jahat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tiap daerah punya versi yang berbeda jauh.\N- Muumuu itu pembela keadilan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Muumuu yang santai juga bagus, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tidak ada kesimpulan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami tulis festival tiap daerah\Ndan ditentukan dengan undian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, undiannya sekali saja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Turnamen Bela Diri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Turnamen bertarung\Ndan menguji kemampuan bela diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira menari, malah ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah saran festivalnya mudah dipahami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mari mulai rencana festivalnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ini festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- kita harus serius menjalankannya!\N- Aku merasa kesannya berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, anggap saja ini seperti lomba olahraga.
